---
// QuickPrintButton - calls window.print() directly
// Styled smaller/gray compared to PrintButton which links to a dedicated route
---
<button
  type="button"
  onclick="window.print()"
  class="no-print inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors"
>
  🖨️ พิมพ์หน้านี้
</button>
